    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Συμβουλευτική Επιτροπή ΕΟΧ"@el, "Coiste Comhairleach LEE"@ga, "Beratender EWR-Ausschuss"@de, "Rådgivande EES-kommittén"@sv, "Comitetul consultativ al SEE"@ro, "Comité Consultivo del EEE"@es, "Poradní výbor EHP"@cs, "Comité Consultivo do EEE"@pt, "EEE konsultacinis komitetas"@lt, "Kumitat Konsultattiv taż-ŻEE"@mt, "Comitato consultivo SEE"@it, "EGT konzultatív bizottság"@hu, "Comité consultatif de l’EEE"@fr, "EMP nõuandekomitee"@et, "Det Rådgivende EØS-Udvalg"@da, "Savjetodavni odbor za EGP"@hr, "Poradný výbor EHP"@sk, "Komitet Konsultacyjny EOG"@pl, "EEZ Konsultatīvā komiteja"@lv, "EEA Consultative Committee"@en, "ETA:n konsultatiivinen komitea"@fi, "Posvetovalni odbor EGP"@sl, "Raadgevend Comité van de EER"@nl, "Консултативен комитет на ЕИП"@bg;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Economic Area Consultative Committee is part of the EEA agreement, and was created when the agreement entered into force in 1994. It represents employers, workers and other civil society players of EEA member states. Non-EU members include Iceland, Liechtenstein and Norway. Switzerland sends observers. The Committee comprises representatives of the European Economic and Social Committee and of the EFTA Consultative Committee. The Committee meets once a year. At each of its meetings, the Committee adopts resolutions and reports related to various aspects of the internal market, as well as to important developments in the EEA. The resolutions are sent to the EEA Council for information."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "EEAREA_CC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "EEAREA_CC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001579"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Komitet Konsultacyjny Europejskiego Obszaru Gospodarczego"@pl, "Comitato consultivo dello Spazio economico europeo"@it, "Posvetovalni odbor Evropskega gospodarskega prostora"@sl, "Poradní výbor Evropského hospodářského prostoru"@cs, "Kumitat Konsultattiv taż-Żona Ekonomika Ewropea"@mt, "Poradný výbor Európskeho hospodárskeho priestoru"@sk, "Comité consultatif de l’Espace économique européen"@fr, "European Economic Area Consultative Committee"@en, "Συμβουλευτική Επιτροπή του Ευρωπαϊκού Οικονομικού Χώρου"@el, "Coiste Comhairleach an Limistéir Eorpaigh Eacnamaíoch"@ga, "Beratender Ausschuss Europäischer Wirtschaftsraum"@de, "Comité Consultivo del Espacio Económico Europeo"@es, "Comitetul consultativ al Spațiului Economic European"@ro, "Консултативен комитет на Европейското икономическо пространство"@bg, "Euroopa Majanduspiirkonna nõuandekomitee"@et, "Savjetodavni odbor za Europski gospodarski prostor"@hr, "Euroopan talousalueen konsultatiivinen komitea"@fi, "Europos ekonominės erdvės konsultacinis komitetas"@lt, "Comité Consultivo do Espaço Económico Europeu"@pt, "Det rådgivende udvalg for Det Europæiske Økonomiske Samarbejdsområde"@da, "Az Európai Gazdasági Térség konzultatív bizottsága"@hu, "Raadgevend Comité van de Europese Economische Ruimte"@nl, "Eiropas Ekonomikas zonas Konsultatīvā komiteja"@lv;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EEAREA_CC_1994_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "EEAREA_CC";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "EEAREA_CC";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "EEAREA_CC";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1994-01-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "EEAREA_CC";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EEAREA>
}
